        "subject": " LU-3406 kernel: new version of raid5-mmp patch",
        "message": " LU-3406 kernel: new version of raid5-mmp patch\n\nThis new version of raid5-mmp patch is an attempt to\nintroduce and use a specific REQ_NOCACHE flag to\nindicate and implement the need of MMP-block read from\ndevice instead from stripe-cache in SW-Raid code, and\nto be used by ext4/ldiskfs.\nWith debug/checks included to verify behavior !!...\n\nTest-Parameters: clientcount=1 osscount=2 mdscount=2 austeroptions=-R failover=true useiscsi=true testgroup=failover\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: I4694e34534156e9cdc40d2ce199065f2867ce8b2\n"
      },
